361
00:21:19,688 --> 00:21:21,688
Grandfather?

362
00:21:24,187 --> 00:21:26,187
You have to sleep now.

363
00:21:26,187 --> 00:21:28,187
I'm not tired.

364
00:21:28,187 --> 00:21:30,187
Are you happy too?

365
00:21:30,187 --> 00:21:32,187
Yes, my child, very happy.

366
00:22:33,351 --> 00:22:47,351
Thank you for watching and see you in the next video.

367
00:22:47,515 --> 00:22:56,515
The next morning Heidi went right after sunrise for the first time in a long,
long time with Peter and the goats up on the meadow.

368
00:22:56,515 --> 00:23:02,515
Again and again Heidi shouted loudly. It was as if she had never seen all of
this before.

369
00:23:02,515 --> 00:23:07,515
The mountains, the clouds, the meadows. Heidi could not grasp her luck.

370
00:23:09,515 --> 00:23:14,417
For hours she lay in the meadow with Peter and enjoyed the sunbeams.

371
00:23:14,417 --> 00:23:17,717
For Heidi, a dream had come true.

372
00:23:17,717 --> 00:23:22,117
Even an eagle saw her on her first day up here on the alp.

373
00:23:22,117 --> 00:23:26,117
But we want to tell you about that in our next story.

